Ifumbire mvaruganda ni imwe mu mafumbire akoreshwa mu [[Rwanda]] mu buhinzi, yongera umusaruro ariko igira ingaruka ku kugundura[gushimura] ubutaka, kwanduza [[Amazi, Isuku n'isukura|amazi]] n’imihindagurikire y’ikirere<ref>https://mobile.igihe.com/ibidukikije/article/hagaragajwe-ingaruka-z-ifumbire-mvaruganda-ku-mihindagurikire-y-ikirere</ref>


== Ifumbire mvaruganda yangiza ibidukikije . ==
Imvaruganda ikunzwe gukoreshwa mu buhinzi bw'ibihingwa bitandukanye mu gihugu hari ikoreshwa babagara imyaka cg bayitera . Haje gukorwa ubushakakashatsi bugaragaza ko ifumbire mvaruganda kubera ikoreshwa ryayo ryishi cyangwa nabi yangiza ibidukikije n'ibinyabuzima biba mubutaka . ifumbire mvaruganda  yangiza ubutaka nttihaboneke umusaruro wari witezwe ndetse no kwanduza [[Amazi, Isuku n'isukura|amazi]] bika byica bimwe mu binyabuzima n'ibimera biba mu mazi<ref>https://flash.rw/2022/01/20/gukoresha-ifumbire-mvaruganda-yonyine-byangiza-ubutaka-ubushakashatsi/</ref> .

== Uburyo abahinzi bagira umusaruro mwiza badakoresheje ifumbire mvaruganda ==
Hamaze gukora ubushakashatsi bywagaragaje ko ifumbire mvaruganda yangiza ibidukikije ikanduza [[Amazi, Isuku n'isukura|amazi]] ibigo bitandukanye byita kubidukijreje byakanguriye abahinzi gukoresha ifumbire y'imborera ,ikomoka kubimera ,ku [[Amatungo|matungo]] ,kubisagazwa bya amatungo,no gukoresha ifumbire nziza itangwa [[Iminyorogoto|n'iminyorogoto]] yatangiye gukoreshwa mu [[Rwanda]] itangiza ibidukikije kandi itanga umusaruro <ref>https://www.kigalitoday.com/amakuru/amakuru-mu-rwanda/article/gukora-ifumbire-yifashishije-iminyorogoto-n-utundi-dukoko-bimuteje-imbere</ref>.

