Hamazwe gukora ubugenzuzi n'ubushakashatsi hasanzwe ifumbire y'imborera ikorwa hifashishijwe [[iminyorogoto]] ari nziza ku bihingwa n'urosobe rw'ibimera n'ibidukikije muri rusange <ref>https://rwanda.shafaqna.com/FR/AL/247900</ref>.

